I have eczema on my eyelids and one time a guy asked another guy to ask me whether i had makeup on cuz my eyelids were bright pink...i never thought someone could think that, usually it's oh is she a burn victim? Whats wrong with her face?...u have to be so careful...i have it all over my face(especially eyes(my nickname is red panda), underneath nose, cheekbones), my arms, fingers, armpit part of my leg, feet, shoulders, collarbones, neck, ears and back oh also on my private part and butt. They can be calm(not noticable) or raging. i sleep with a 1litre tub of moisturiser next to my head lol. When ppl ask what i couldnt live without i would say cream. I think it will get better when i become an adult...the scars wont leave but eh. I actually thought all my eczema scars were birthmarks until recently
